<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Home</title>
    <meta
      name="author"
      content="paul mondl (isdadev) & phillip schlichting (philrico)"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
  </head>
  <body id="home">
    <main>
      <div class="header-section">
        <header>
          <nav>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
              <li><a href="/gallery">Gallery</a></li>
              <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
          </nav>
        </header>
        <div class="media">
          <video muted id="header-video-1" autoplay>
            <source src="assets/video.mp4" />
          </video>
          <img
            src="assets/header-image-1.png"
            alt="headerimg1"
            id="header-image-1"
          />
          <img
            src="assets/header-image-2.png"
            alt="headerimg2"
            id="header-image-2"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="cta-button">
          <button><a href="#COTD-section">Learn more</a></button>
        </div>
        <div class="control-button">
          <div class="button-left">
            <button id="control-button-left">
              <img src="assets/arrow-left.png" alt="" height="30px" />
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="button-right">
            <button id="control-button-right">
              <img src="assets/arrow-right.png" alt="" height="30px" />
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="image-section">
            <img src="assets/logo.jpeg" alt="intro image" />
          </div>
          <div class="text-section">
            <h1>About us</h1>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <h2>Who are we?</h2>
              </li>
              <p>
                At Project MOSC, we are a dedicated team of automotive designers
                and racing enthusiasts united by our love for speed and
                innovation. Our diverse backgrounds in engineering, graphic
                design, and motorsport allow us to push the boundaries of
                racecar design.
                <br />
                We believe that every racecar tells a unique story, and we aim
                to showcase this through captivating designs that represent the
                thrill of racing. As a close-knit community, we draw inspiration
                from the vibrant world of motorsport, inspiring professionals
                and enthusiasts alike with our creativity and craftsmanship.
                <br />
                Join us on our journey as we celebrate the intersection of art
                and engineering, continually redefining what's possible in
                racecar design.
              </p>
              <li>
                <h2>What are we trying to achieve?</h2>
              </li>
              <p>
                Our mission is to educate and inspire. We share our passion for
                racecars with both enthusiasts and newcomers, fostering a deeper
                understanding of the artistry, engineering, and history behind
                these incredible machines.
                <br />
                Through engaging content and stunning presentations, we
                highlight the unique features and innovations of each racecar.
                We also showcase our designs, inviting our audience to
                appreciate the beauty and performance of these vehicles.
                <br />
                Together, we aim to create a community where knowledge and
                passion intersect, celebrating the rich heritage of racecars
                while paving the way for future innovations in design and
                performance.
              </p>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="COTD-section" id="COTD-section">
        <h2>We present you the car of the month</h2>
        <div class="COTD">
          <div class="card" data-class="<%= randomCar['class'] %>">
            <div class="carImg">
              <a
                href="/gallery/<%= randomCar['uid'] %>"
                class="carClass <%= randomCar['uid'] %>"
                ><img src="<%= randomCar['image_url'] %>" alt="Racecar"
              /></a>
            </div>
            <div class="textSection1">
              <h3><%= randomCar["name"] %></h3>
              <div></div>
              <h3><%= randomCar["brand"] %></h3>
              <h4><%= randomCar["class"] %></h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
      <p>&copy; 2024 MOSC</p>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <p><a href="/impressum">impressum</a></p>
        <p><a href="/privacy">privacy</a></p>
      </div>
    </footer>
    <script src="scripts/functionality.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
